    P9 --> P10["Phase 10: Deep Review"]
    P10 --> P11["Phase 11: Report Assembly"]

    P11 --> C["Cleanup graphify MCP server via audit-output/graph/mcp.pid"]
    P11 --> R["CONFIRMED-REPORT.md"]
